As of now, user have to click on each ticket to see the status of each ticket on the calendar.
 * When task deadlines are displayed in the calendar, one can hover over the task placeholder (usually a red or green rectangle) to see which task is due on a given date, however there is no indicator to the task's status. Instead one has to click on every task to check its status. It would be great if the task status could be displayed as part of the hover, so one can get a quick overview of which tasks whose deadlines are approaching are still in the pipeline (as opposed to already resolved).

Having the ability to display the status of the ticket will be useful for users and improve user experience.

