h3. Problem Definition

The Issue Types and Projects menus on the ConfigureCustomField!default.jspa page are only tall enough to display 5 options. In addition, the Issue Types menu is not alphabetized (documented in JRA-61108). With a long list of issue types and/or projects to associate, it is very tedious to make all of the selections and also very easy to accidentally select the wrong issue type or project.

h3. Suggested Solution

The customer would like the select list menus to be taller so that more options are visible and less scrolling is required, making the menus easier to use and reducing the chance that the wrong issue type or project is selected.

{quote}
My request is very reasonable and extremely simple. For each of these two select lists (issue types and projects) there is a parameter set as
size="5"
All the developers would have to do is change that to
size="25" 
{quote}

